      "text": "Ah, about two, three years.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after this, Schindler had come-- he come.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Schindler had come, and had tell he wants some people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No change.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was the same.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing you can do.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to do it what they say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no, nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The same.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We go together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When he-- we-- if he was going, I'll go with him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 157,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 158,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I tell you what.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What's happened like-- for Schindler, you see, Schindler come.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He go to the bus when it come from the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He tell them, I want people.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
